<L>__{interior shipboard operating room night}
<A>__{ishmael feverish, writhing unconscious against the straps that hold him to a table. all around him, a hell of men and blood and doctors and limbs and shouted curses they never showed us on m.a.s.h.}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{my arm was dealt with by a pharmacist's mate, whose surgical career was four hours old.}
<A>__{ishmael lurches, his eyes pop open, wild and bleary...}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{he used a handsaw.}
<A>__{...seeing there, in a corner, on a pile of blood soaked dressings... ...his left arm.}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{i dream of it, now and then. the way my fingers curled. against the wall.}
<A>__{he blinks at it. realizing at last that the arm is his...}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{...fucking goddam jap bitch !}
<A>__{an orderly turns at the words. nods. as if he knows.}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{it was all i could think of to say.}
<A>__{his eyes squeeze shut.}
<C>__{ishmael }
<D>__{there was nothing more to say. for a long while.}
